org.apache.paimon.table

Class FallbackReadFileStoreTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.table.DelegatedFileStoreTable
      • org.apache.paimon.table.FallbackReadFileStoreTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, DataTable, FileStoreTable, InnerTable, Table

    public class FallbackReadFileStoreTable
extends DelegatedFileStoreTable
    A FileStoreTable which mainly read from the current branch. However, if the current branch does not have a partition, it will read that partition from the fallback branch.
    See Also:
